    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but sitting with it doesn't change anything. it just makes the weight heavier. i've tried sitting with it, i've tried fighting it, i've tried fixing it... and nothing changes. it's just the same loop. the only way to actually stop the cycle, the only way to make it quiet, is to just break it once and for all.",
